  "texts": [
    "Participants who failed at least one of two attention checks were excluded from the analyses (n = 7).",
    "The 120 participants in the final sample were 37.2 ± 13.2 (mean ± std) years old and 50% of them identified as female.",
    "Participants first indicated their preferences for different iPhone ads.",
    "The ad messages were tailored to the high and low ends of the Big Five personality traits using the open-source playground version of GPT-3 (version \"text-davinci-003\").",
    "For example, we prompted GPT-3 to generate an iPhone ad tailored to Extraversion with the prompt: \"Write an iPhone ad for someone who is extraverted and enthusiastic\"."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}